---
// §9 — Self-host / ownership. PAS resolution + risk reversal + real quickstart.
---
<section id="self-host" class="section">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="copy reveal-up">
      <p class="kicker"><span class="kicker-dot"></span>Self-host</p>
      <h2 class="h2">Your wiki, on your machine.</h2>
      <p class="lede">No SaaS account, no seat pricing, no data on someone else's servers. Clone, set three secrets, and run.</p>
      <p class="reassure">Your markdown lives in SQLite on a volume you control. Open code — read exactly what runs before you run it.</p>
      <a class="docs-link" href="https://github.com/zcag/tela#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read the docs →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="quick reveal-up">
      <div class="q-head">
        <span class="q-dot"></span><span class="q-dot"></span><span class="q-dot"></span>
        <span class="q-title">quickstart</span>
      </div>
      <pre class="q-code" tabindex="0" aria-label="quickstart commands"><code><span class="c"># 1 — set TELA_PUBLIC_BASE_URL + 2 secrets</span>
cp deploy/.env.example deploy/.env

<span class="c"># 2 — backend + frontend + Caddy on :8780</span>
make up</code></pre>
      <div class="q-foot">
        <span class="q-pill">one binary</span>
        <span class="q-pill">SQLite + FTS5</span>
        <span class="q-pill">no Postgres</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; align-items: center; }
  .reassure { margin-top: 1.4rem; max-width: var(--measure); color: var(--fg-soft); font-size: var(--text-base); line-height: var(--leading-normal); }
  .docs-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.2rem; color: var(--brand); font-size: var(--text-base); }
  .docs-link:hover { color: var(--brand-strong); text-decoration: underline; }

  .quick {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--surface-sunk);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .q-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    height: 38px;
    padding: 0 0.9rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .q-dot { width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: var(--radius-full); background: var(--border-strong); }
  .q-title { margin-left: 0.4rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--fg-faint); }
  .q-code {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--fg);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .q-code .c { color: var(--fg-faint); }
  .q-foot { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0 1.1rem 1.1rem; }
  .q-pill {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--fg-soft);
  }
  @media (min-width: 920px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; } }
</style>
